where_conditions: WHERE display_name = 'Continuous Renal Replacement Therapy' and quest_name = 'JHM IP CRRT TYPE'
WHERE display_name = 'Continuous Renal Replacement Therapy' and quest_name like '%ULTRAFILTRATION%'
WHERE display_name = 'Continuous Renal Replacement Therapy' and (quest_name like '%INITIAL FLOW RATE%' or (quest_name like '%BLOOD FLOW RATE%' and ord_quest_resp like '%initial setup%'))
WHERE display_name = 'Continuous Renal Replacement Therapy' and (quest_name like '%TITRATE BLOOD FLOW RATE%' or (quest_name like '%BLOOD FLOW RATE%' and not ord_quest_resp like '%initial setup%'))
WHERE "diagname" ~* 'stroke' and not "diagname" ~* 'due to stroke|effect of stroke'
where diagname ~ 'UTI' or diagname ~* 'urinary tract infection|urosepsis|pyelo'
where diagname ~* 'pneumonia|acute lung injury|empyema|acute respiratory distress syndrome' or  diagname ~ 'ARDS|ALI'
where diagname ~* 'biliary sepsis|cholecystitis|ascending cholangitis|cholelithiasis|gall stones|hepatic absess|cholangitis'

where diagname ~* 'intra abdominal sepsis|abdominal catastrophe|perforated viscous|free air|pneumoperitoneum|pneumotosis|peritonitis|spontaneous bacterial peritonitis|gut translocation|c. diff|colitis|peritoneal abscess|clostridium difficile'

where lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"% uti %"}') and not lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"%history of uti%","% ho uti%","% ro uti%","% r/o uti%","%suggestive of uti%","%hx of uti%","%uti resolved%"}')

where lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"%pneumonia%","% pna %", "% cap %","%sputum culture for afb%"}') and not lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"%history of[a-z ,]*pneumonia%","%evaluate for pneumonia%","%hx of pneumonia%","%h/o pneumonia%","%r/o [a-z ,]*pneumonia%"}')

dbtable: (select first("CSN_ID") as visit_id, first("PROC_START_TIME") as tsp, json_build_object('frequency', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'FrequencyOfOrder'), 'priority', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'priority'), 'ORDER_TIME', first("ORDER_TIME"), 'RESULT_TIME', first("RESULT_TIME"), 'ParentOrderTime', first("ParentOrderTime"), 'PROC_START_TIME', first("PROC_START_TIME"), 'PROC_ENDING_TIME', first("PROC_ENDING_TIME"), 'ParentStartTime', first("ParentStartTime"), 'ParentEndingTime', first("ParentEndingTime")) as value from $clarity_workspace."OrderProcs_643" where proc_name ~* 'cpap' or (proc_name ~ 'NON-INVASIVE VENTILATION' and ord_quest_resp ~* 'cpap') group by "INSTNTD_ORDER_ID") A

(select first("CSN_ID") as visit_id, first("PROC_START_TIME") as tsp, json_build_object('frequency', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'FrequencyOfOrder'), 'priority', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'priority'), 'ORDER_TIME', first("ORDER_TIME"), 'RESULT_TIME', first("RESULT_TIME"), 'ParentOrderTime', first("ParentOrderTime"), 'PROC_START_TIME', first("PROC_START_TIME"), 'PROC_ENDING_TIME', first("PROC_ENDING_TIME"), 'ParentStartTime', first("ParentStartTime"), 'ParentEndingTime', first("ParentEndingTime")) as value from $clarity_workspace."OrderProcs_643" where proc_name ~ 'MECHANICAL VENTILATION' and not proc_name ~* 'cpap' group by "INSTNTD_ORDER_ID")  as sub
